author: AP, AP
title: Mom of T-Wolves Star Karl-Anthony Towns Dies from Coronavirus
description: MINNEAPOLIS (AP) — Jacqueline Cruz-Towns, the mother of Minnesota Timberwolves center Karl-Anthony Towns, died Monday due to complications from COVID-19 after more than a month of fighting the virus. She was 59.
